  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC459">
        <l>oruporu ḷirucoṟ pirivila varaiyār.</l>
            </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/253/mode/1up">253</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/253/mode/1up">253</ref>.</p>
<p>ic cūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, ituvum marapuvaḻuk kāttatu.</p>
<p>urai : oru poruṇmēṟ kiṭanta irucoṟ piriviṉṟiniṉṟaṉa varaiyappaṭātu eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu :</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC459-Iḷam-cit1">
<l>'vaiyaik kiḻavaṉ vayaṅkutār māṇakalan</l>
<l>taiyalā yiṉṟunī nalkuti nalkāyēṟ</l>
<l>kūṭalār kōvoṭu nīyum paṭutiyō</l>
<l>nāṭaṟiyak kavvai yoruṅku'</l></lg>
<p>vaiyaikku iṟai yeṉappaṭṭāṉum, kō eṉappaṭṭāṉum avaṉātalāl, avvirucollum oru poruṭkaṇmēlē niṉṟaṉa ; piṟa poruṭkup piriyā, aṅṅaṉam niṟpaṉa amaiyum eṉpatām.</p>
<p>iṉip, 'pirivila varaiyappaṭā' eṉavē, pirivuṭaiyaṉa varaiyappaṭum eṉpatām ; aḵtiyātō veṉiṉ,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC459-Iḷam-cit2">
<l>'koytaḷirt taṇṭalaik kūṟṟap peruñcēntaṉ</l>
<l>vaikalu mēṟum vayakkaḷiṟē - kaitoḻutēṉ</l>
<l>kālēka vaṇṇaṉaik kaṇṇārak kāṇaveñ</l>
<l>cālēkañ cāra naṭa'</l></lg>
<p>itaṉuḷ, 'kūṟṟapperuñ cēntaṉ' eṉṟār, piṉṉaik 'kālēka vaṇṇaṉ' eṉṟār ; avai yiraṇṭu collum pirivuṭaiya, ataṉāṉ amaiyā ; yātō piriveṉiṉ, 'kālēkavaṇṇam' eṉpatu cāntu, kūṟṟapperuñ cēntaṟkē yurittāy niṟpatoṉṟaṉṟu. 'kālēkavaṇṇam' eṉṉuñ cāntu pūciṉārk kellāṅ kālēkavaṇṇar eṉṟu peyarām, ataṉāṟ pirivuṭaittu ; ātalāl, amaiyātu eṉpatu.</p>
<p>mēṟ kiḷaviyākkattu,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC459-Iḷam-cit3">
<l>'iyaṟpeyark kiḷaviyuñ cuṭṭuppeyark kiḷaviyum'</l>	<p>[tol. col. kiḷavi - 38]</p></lg>
<p>eṉṟum,</p>	
<lg xml:id="TolC459-Iḷam-cit4">
<l>'ciṟappi ṉākiya peyarnilaik kiḷavikku'</l>	<p>[tol. col. kiḷavi - 41]</p></lg>
<p>eṉṟum,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC459-Iḷam-cit5">
<l>'oruporuḷ kuṟitta vēṟupeyark kiḷavi'</l>	<p>[tol. col. kiḷavi - 42]</p></lg>
<p>eṉṟum oruporuṇmēl irupeyar vaḻuvum, pala peyar vaḻuvum kūṟip pōntāṉ ; avaṟṟōṭitaṉiṭai vēṟṟumai terintukoḷka.	(63)</p>
 </body>
  </text>

